2015-05-15 Ryuichiro Nakato <rnakato@iam.u-tokyo.ac.jp>
	Version 3.0.0 (Beta)
	- refine the program and add new functions.
	- Main improvements are:
          -- improve the speed and memory consumed.
          -- multiple input files are allowed for parse2wig.
	  -- bedGraph and bigWig become available.
	  -- allow peak-calling without Input sample.
	  -- output various stats of input sample.
	  -- several functions are newly added.
        - See Manual for details of the functions.

