2014-09-29 Ryuichiro Nakato <rnakato@iam.u-tokyo.ac.jp>
	Version 2.6.0
	- parse2wig2: become to use background regions only when calculating genome coverage with '-igpeak' option
	- remove '-normgc' option for parse2wig2 and add '-normgcov' option for drompa2, which normalizes the reads with the genome coverage for windows with fixed lengh
	- parse2wig2 becomes to output genome coverage files 'Gcov' in the output directory

